EXTRACTED VALUE: We have never had any trouble getting a window seat, or any kind of rudeness from the staff. May 07, we'll be back! Thank you Bull Shed.
Service, food, view - all excellent. The best.
It came highly recommended by my local contacts, but I think this is because it has become an "institution" per se.
And the best part? I don't have to empty my entire bank account for a nice dinner out here. What's not to like?
